Statement = If you want the output to be in the same line and have a space separate them,

We can add an empty space between the format specifiers to output space separated values.
Task
Write a program which does the following

Output the result of 3 + 4
Output the result of 2 + 1 on the same line separated by a space from the previous result

Sol.= 
#include<stdio.h>

int main() {
    
    printf("%d %d", 3+4, 2+1);
    
    return 0;
}
